{"tid":2057940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Google是鬼？","createTime":"2020-06-09T18:34:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T18:48:10.000Z","uid":171506,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8ff748771873919ead41d7d6257a4fb843b9bbfb","tid":2057940,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T18:34:28.000Z","msg":"Google 最近疑點重重。<br />\n<br />\n最新的是，今天 Google 被發現，只要在搜尋框隨便輸入亂碼，就會在搜尋建議中跳出之前總統選舉時，國民黨鋪天蓋地在抹黑陳菊的所謂氣爆善款案。<br />\n<br />\n再往前看有什麼呢？<br />\n<br />\nYouTube 被抓包長期自動刪除包含「共匪」或「五毛」字樣的留言。根據 The Verge 的說法，YouTube 至少從去年十月就開始刪除相關的留言了。<br />\n<br />\n報導 &rarr;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/137869\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com.tw%2Fnews%2F137869&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XelgxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=d300de19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/137869</a><br />\n<br />\n另外是 #Google翻譯 上個月開始，忽然全面以中國用語取代台灣用語，並在旁邊標上「社群認證」標章。翻譯 video 會獲得「視頻」、翻譯 software 會獲得「軟件」⋯⋯等，族繁不及備載。<br />\n<br />\n報導 &rarr; <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BerryVoice/posts/3014567928622541\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FBerryVoice%2Fposts%2F3014567928622541&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XelgxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=ecdb7187\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/BerryVoice/posts/3014567928622541</a><br />\n<br />\nYouTube 的事件 Google 推給演算法了，但翻譯的事件至今沒有講過半句話。而這次跳針「陳菊 善款」的事件又要找什麼藉口呢？<br />\n<br />\n我想問：Google 到底還要躲在「演算法」後面多久、還要噤聲多久？"},{"pid":"e03bd8dcf7c013e36b443901910544c8f2bb2310","tid":2057940,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T18:35:45.000Z","msg":"轉載，不是我寫的"},{"pid":"e5b8b9be59fe0b50cd4373bfb31fc8529cfdac02","tid":2057940,"uid":171506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T18:39:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157093414550877&amp;id=551090876\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10157093414550877%26id%3D551090876&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XelgxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=b21eb9fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157093414550877&amp;id=551090876</a><br />\n<br />\n原文出處"},{"pid":"47da59ade9f6d507c6c8611de8ae3ab70f783a9e","tid":2057940,"uid":59976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T18:40:38.000Z","msg":"be evil<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"912b1011849d6f6713758aaba1c2b69d588f8768","tid":2057940,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T18:41:57.000Z","msg":"鬼咗好耐啦"},{"pid":"4229d1320454b2f84ad2703215dc4d4bae51994c","tid":2057940,"uid":287329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T18:43:09.000Z","msg":"Google 條印度佬根本有問題<br />\nYouTube奶到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9264d6e091943a2da7a602ac121f3da50e49c210","tid":2057940,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47da59ade9f6d507c6c8611de8ae3ab70f783a9e","tid":2057940,"uid":59976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T18:40:38.000Z","msg":"be evil<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T18:43:15.000Z","msg":"RedTube"},{"pid":"48f55371036c40801de1ae54aa1ee080e227c51e","tid":2057940,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47da59ade9f6d507c6c8611de8ae3ab70f783a9e","tid":2057940,"uid":59976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T18:40:38.000Z","msg":"be evil<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T18:48:10.000Z","msg":"菇變evil"}]}